 INSTALL FROM GIT
==================

 Git version
-------------
git clone git://git.vtoc.de/vagra
ln -s vagra/Makefile.inc

edit Makefile.inc

set compiler/linker flags suitable for your system

make sure the following modules are enabled:

MODULES = article comment user passwd

run "make" or "gmake" if your make version does not support GNU extension


 Postgres
----------
$ psql
CREATE DATABASE vablo; 
CREATE USER vablo WITH ENCRYPTED PASSWORD 'changeme';

$ psql vablo < vablo.sql


 tntnet
--------
cp tnt/vagra.conf.default tnt/vagra.conf
edit tnt/vagra.conf

the tnt subdirectory contains all neded at runtime, just copy it to server and run:
$ tntnet -c tntnet.xml

Login https://maya:8443/admin/
	User:	admin
	Passwd:	vablo
